title: War of the Roses: The Orange Thong
description: Kendall came home from a girls weekend to see a little bit of water in her and her boyfriend, Mike, jacuzzi tub.  Neither of them use the tub so she asked Mike if he had and he said no and didn't know where the water came from.  Then something happened when their dog was going number 2 in the yard that is leading Kendall to believe that Mike was up to something while she was out of town.
